  <brief_title>Atazanavir or Lopinavir in HIV Post-exposure Prophylaxis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of 2 Alternative Antiretroviral Combinations in HIV Post-exposure Prophylaxis: AZT-3TC (Combivir速) + Lopinavir-ritonavir (Kaletra速) Versus AZT-3TC (Combivir速)+ Atazanavir (Reyataz速). Multicentre, Prospective, Randomized, Open Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hospital Clinic of Barcelona</agency>
