    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Hospital Clinic of Barcelona</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study compares the adherence of 240 HIV-negative subjects randomly assigned to 2
      different antiretroviral therapies for 28 days after accidental exposure to HIV.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
